quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  42,51,"Tekisaanirangako muntu Katonda kwogera naye, okugyako nga amusaako bubaka, oba nayogera naye nga asinziira mabega wa kintu ekyawulawo, oba okutuma omubaka (Malayika), olwo nno kulwokusalawokwe namutumira kyaba ayagadde (anti) mazima yye wa waggulu nnyo mugoba nsonga"
  42,52,"Nabwekityo twakutumira (ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) omwoyo (Kur’ani eyitibwa mwoyo wano olwokuba yeewa emyooyo gy’abantu obulamu) nga ekyo kisinziira ku kiragiro kyaffe. Wali tomanyi nti ekitabo (Kur’ani) kye ki, wadde obukkiriza naye twagifuula ekitangaala nga tulungamya nayo oyo gwetuba twagadde mu baddu baffe, era mazima ggwe ddala olungamya eri ekkubo eggolokofu"
  42,53,Ekkubo lya Katonda oyo bibye yekka ebiri mu ggulu omusanvu nebyo ebiri mu nsi. Abange eri Katonda ebintu byonna gye bidda
  43,1,Ha Miim
  43,2,Ndayidde ekitabo ekinnyonnyofu
  43,3,Mazima ffe twagissa Kur’ani nga eri mu luwarabu oba olyawo ne mutegeera
  43,4,Era mazima yo eri ku nsibuko ye bitabo (Lauhul mahfudh) ddala yo ya waggulu nnyo ejjudde amagezi
  43,5,Abaffe tunabajjirako ddala okubuulirira olwokuba muli abantu abasukka ekikemo (abatagoberera mateeka ga Katonda)
  43,6,Bameka ba Nabbi betwatuma mu baasooka
  43,7,Tewali Nabbi yenna yabajjira okugyako bamujeejanga
  43,8,Olwo nno netuzikiriza abamaanyi okusinga abo (abakafiiri be Makkah) era ekyatuuka ku baakulembera kimanyiddwa (abalala bandikitutte nga ekyokuyiga)
  43,9,"Singa obabuuza nti ani yatonda eggulu omusanvu ne nsi, ddala bajja kugamba nti yabitonda nantakubwa ku mukono omumanyi ennyo"
  43,10,Oyo eyabateerawo ensi nga nyanjuluze nagibateeramu amakubo mulyoke mulungame (mutuuke gye mulaga)
  43,11,Era oyo assa okuva waggulu amazzi nga ga kigero (ekyetaagisa) netuzza bugya nago ekitundu ekifu (olwekyeya) bwemutyo bwe mulifulumizibwa (nga muzuukira)
  43,12,Era yooyo eyatonda emitindo ebiri ebiri gyonna era nabateerawo amaato n’ebisolo ebyawaka ebyo bye mwebagala
  43,13,"Mube nga mutebenkera ku migongo gyazo, oluvanyuma musiime ekyengera kya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe wemuzituulirako, era mugambe nti, musukkulumu oyo eyatugondeza kino tetwandibadde bakisobola"
  43,14,Era mazima ddala ffe tuli ba kudda ewa Mukama omulabirizi waffe
  43,15,"Naye abatakkiriza bateeka ku Katonda abamu ku baddube (nti nabo ba Katonda), mazima omuntu mwewakanyi omweyolefu"
  43,16,Oba mwebyo byatonda mweyasalawo okwegyira abawala ate mmwe naasalawo okubawa abalenzi
  43,17,So nga omu kubo bwaba aweereddwa amawulire nti afunye omwana agwa mu kiti kyabo be bapaatiika ku Katonda ekyenyi kye kisiiba kifumye era nga naye munyiikaavu
  43,18,"Abaffe oyo akuzibwa ng’ali mu bya kwenyiriza, era nga yye mu kunnyonnyola taba na nsonga nywevu (gwemuwa Katonda)"
  43,19,"Ba Malayika abo, abaddu ba Katonda omusaasizi ne babafuula abakazi! abaffe baaliwo nga batondwa? Obujulizi bwabwe (bwe bepampalika okuwa) bujja kuwandiikibwa era bagenda kubuuzibwa"
  43,20,"Era bagamba nti singa Katonda omusaasizi ennyo yayagala tetwandibasinzizza ekyo tebakirinaako kumanya kwonna, tebali (mu kukola ekyo) okugyako bateebereza buteebereza"
  43,21,Abaffe twabawa ekitabo oluberyeberye lwakino (ekikolwa kyabwe) balyoke babe nga kye bekwatako
  43,22,"Wabula bagamba nti mazima ffe twasanga baganda baffe nga bali ku nkola, era mazima ffe tuli ku buwufu bwabwe kwe tulungamira"
  43,23,"Nabwekityo tetwatuma luberyeberyelwo mu kitundu kyonna mutiisa okugyako nga babinojjo baamu bagamba nti mazima ffe twasanga bakadde baffe nga bali ku nkola, era mazima ffe tuli ku buwufu bwabwe tugoberera"